Title: Object: Entrée de Buonaparte en Egypte
Description: Napoleon, mounted at the head of his expeditionary force, offered the keys to Alexandria by two Muslim officials, supported by a small armed guard and a few citizens and merchants; walled city in background. Etching and engraving, hand-coloured
Associated names: Associated with: Napoléon I, Emperor of the French (Napoleon)
Associated events: Associated Event: French occupation of Egypt 1798
